						<div class="pdf-file">
				<a href="/fr/content/download/255832/3078286/file/3cb4f93e53e5d2786ae109e4800de520.pdf">Télécharger <img src="/extension/agritrade/design/agritrade/images/pdf.gif" alt="" /></a>
